title: [Cysaegir, Brook]
description: A quaint bungalow rests quietly alongside a bubbling brook teeming with an assortment of fish and other aquatic life, creating a picture perfect scene.  Fiddlehead ferns surround the brook on all sides, and the light of the moon softly illuminates clusters of glossy-leafed holly trees.
